{"error":0,"message":"","data":[{"show_ID":"2201","airdate":"1583434800","name_switch":"off","DJ":"ziona and Slaygon","showname":"Think on a spring...","blurb":"Hello there! \n\nDear Diary, you would never believe, but spring has arrived! Only technically yet, since there is no difference when it comes to the weather around here, but let's hope for some sun and great remixes soon! \n\nFebruary is over so we have our Remix News section too with Lea! Make sure you won't miss it! \n\nJoin us and SLAY tuned! ","nice_showname":"<strong><big>ziona and Slaygon<\/big><\/strong><br \/>Think on a spring...","nice_airdate":"Thursday 5th March, 2020<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"2202","airdate":"1583607600","name_switch":"off","DJ":"Remix64.com","showname":"Remixer of the Year Awards 2019","blurb":"Yet again, we celebrate and acknowledge the work of the remixers in the C64 and Amiga community by presenting the yearly ROTY Awards, as voted by the users at remix64.com.\n\nThis year it's SceneSat Radio's turn to give out the awards and give you a run-down of what happened in 2019.\nAs usual the show will be jointly broadcast on SLAY Radio and SceneSat Radio, and show chat will be on EFNet in the channel #remix64.","nice_showname":"<strong><big>Remix64.com<\/big><\/strong><br \/>Remixer of the Year Awards 2019","nice_airdate":"Saturday 7th March, 2020<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"}]}